OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783864144
OL,3,C'Is everything okay?': Texts show
OL,4,CWiddecombe went quiet after suspected
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FAnn Widdecombe stopped replying to
OL,8,Fmessages minutes before police believe
OL,9,Fshe was attacked, texts seen by ITV
OL,10,FNews reveal.
OL,12,FA producer was discussing with the
OL,13,Fformer MP her scheduled appearance on
OL,14,FChannel 5's Matt Allwright show on
OL,15,FWednesday afternoon.
OL,17,FIn a WhatsApp conversation shared with
OL,18,FITV News, the producer is discussing
OL,19,Fwith Widdecombe details about the
OL,20,Fappearance and asks her to join a Zoom
OL,21,Fcall from her home.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
