PN,31202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783864144
OL,3,C'Is everything okay?': Texts show
OL,4,CWiddecombe went quiet after suspected
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FThe conversation shows they were
OL,8,Fregularly exchanging messages between
OL,9,F12.14pm and 12.19pm on Wednesday.
OL,11,FThe last message Widdecombe sent at
OL,12,F12.19pm said: "Received! Panic over!!".
OL,14,FA WhatsApp read receipt shows
OL,15,FWiddecombe read a response sent at
OL,16,F12.19pm but did not read any of the
OL,17,Fsubsequent messages from the producer,
OL,18,Fwith the first follow-up sent at
OL,19,F12.48pm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
