FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783864144
OL,3,C'Is everything okay?': Texts show
OL,4,CWiddecombe went quiet after suspected
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FThe producer attempted to call
OL,8,FWiddecombe numerous times but received
OL,9,Fno answer.
OL,11,FAt 12.55pm the producer said: "Hi Ann
OL,12,Fis everything ok?".
OL,14,FAt 1.27pm Allwright confirmed live on
OL,15,Fhis show that Widdecombe was scheduled
OL,16,Fas a guest, but that she had not
OL,17,Fturned up.
OL,19,FThe show's production team followed up
OL,20,Fwith Widdecombe's agent later on
OL,21,FWednesday and again on Thursday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
