PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783864144
OL,3,C'Is everything okay?': Texts show
OL,4,CWiddecombe went quiet after suspected
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FAll of the WhatsApp messages have been
OL,8,Fpassed on to the police.
OL,10,FDevon and Cornwall Police said on
OL,11,FSaturday it is believed Widdecombe was
OL,12,Fattacked on Wednesday at around
OL,13,F12.30pm.
OL,15,FThe ex-Tory prisons minister was found
OL,16,Fdead at her home in Haytor on Dartmoor
OL,17,Fat around 11.40am on Thursday after
OL,18,Fsustaining serious injuries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
