PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783864144
OL,3,C'Is everything okay?': Texts show
OL,4,CWiddecombe went quiet after suspected
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FWiddecombe appeared on TalkTV on
OL,8,FWednesday morning, discussing the by-
OL,9,Felection in Clacton.
OL,11,FA 26-year-old man arrested on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of murdering Widdecombe was
OL,13,Freleased from custody on Saturday and
OL,14,Fis no longer part of the investigation.
OL,16,FAssistant Chief Constable Matt Longman
OL,17,Fsaid on Saturday: "Our inquiries are
OL,18,Fmoving at pace for a suspect who is
OL,19,Fbelieved to be a white male."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
