OL,3,C'Is everything okay?': Texts show
OL,4,CWiddecombe went quiet after suspected
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FWiddecombe was a Conservative MP
OL,8,Fbetween 1987 and 2010 for the Kent
OL,9,Fconstituency of Maidstone, later
OL,10,FMaidstone and the Weald, and held
OL,11,Fseveral ministerial positions in Sir
OL,12,FJohn Major's government.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
