PN,31207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1783864144
OL,3,C'Is everything okay?': Texts show
OL,4,CWiddecombe went quiet after suspected
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FIn her post-Commons career, she
OL,8,Fappeared on the BBC's Strictly Come
OL,9,FDancing in 2010, partnered with Anton
OL,10,Fdu Beke, and reached the semi-finals
OL,11,Fthanks to the public vote.
OL,13,FShe became a member of Nigel Farage's
OL,14,FBrexit Party in 2019 and served as an
OL,15,FMEP representing South West England in
OL,16,FBrussels between 2019 and 2020.
OL,18,FShe later became the immigration and
OL,19,Fjustice spokeswoman for Farage's
OL,20,FReform UK and remained active in the
OL,21,Fmedia.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
